Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:39.53,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Our encounter becomes thy fortune's end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:43.70,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Though words doth joined
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.29,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,From my lips run over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:54.26,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Can yet any convey the truth I hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:57.84,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,As cherry blossoms doth dance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.39,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,To this life I bid farewell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:04.89,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed this body, parent-hatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:08.06,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,I cherish duly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:11.65,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,But graver than life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:15.61,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, smile-clad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:20.03,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Put forth battle, such my scars not fade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.91,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready I stand
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:29.50,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,To draw is to return, the sword and sheath, to cut what is the battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:36.63,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,The heart of the dream abyss-fallen lies bestial
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:43.68,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,If we share such seething blood as we face,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:47.68,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, my love,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.65,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver the finishing blow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:59.61,op_english,,0000,0000,0000,,Dost thou lament the flowers' bloom?
