Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:46.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The strange task she is performing started three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:52.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,when she and the 7th generation Kyotouryuu head Yasuri Shichika arrived here at Hyakkeijou in Oushuu,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:04:00.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and met the 10th sword Seitou Hakari's owner, Higaki Rinne.
