Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:11.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyakkeijou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:19.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where everyone in Hida Takahito's rebellion was publicly executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a land of fate for these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:28.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:30.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it's being compressed or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:35.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like something important to me is being trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:04:59.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:10.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that my homeland would be in such a state when I finally came back to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:11.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:17.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is there really a holy man living in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:20.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like anyone can survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:27.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go check out the nearby towns?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:35.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Higaki Rinne is here, just hidden from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mea—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is there a girl here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:46.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:49.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since I was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:55.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well anyway, pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Higaki Rinne.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:02.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Higaki Rinne?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:08.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The holy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:14.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Togame-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:19.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, you don't even have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're after Seitou Hakari, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:22.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:28.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's buried over there, so go ahead and dig it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably about 30 meters underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:34.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to do it yourself of course, Togame-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right underneath where you're standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:40.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:05.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:20.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:23.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to dig 30 meters by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happened to your schemes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.40,0:07:31.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd have come up with some plan to negotiate with Higaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:32.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:40.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even since finding Higaki Rinne, you've been acting really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:45.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me to just watch you being cornered like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:48.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.98,0:07:55.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Higaki Rinne, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yasuri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:10.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-chan is in her own little world digging, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you went and buried Hakari 30 meters underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bury Seitou Hakari?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:24.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And throwing away something that a friend gave me would be kind of rude, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:27.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just the most convenient way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:28.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it from a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.59,0:08:29.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From Shikizaki Kiki himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From Shikizaki Kiki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, how old are you??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:39.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Around 300 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,350 if you include the time I was human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a holy man here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.42,0:09:15.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I fundamentally avoid things of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:19.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sort of feel like I know you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:24.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because of how you're seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What you're seeing is a projection of your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:29.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Projection of my memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:35.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, a true perception based on your true memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakari doesn't have anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:44.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People look past my own existence and see a perception of their own memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:47.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with me here, we don't really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:49.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what a holy man is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is a holy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.59,0:09:59.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, in a word, a holy man is something like a mirror to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:04.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic mirror that reflects the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:07.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri-kun, have you heard of this foreign fairytale?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.85,0:10:08.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:11.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a far off land there lived a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:14.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a mirror that she always asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:20.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mirror, mirror on the wall, who is the fairest one of all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:28.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The queen wanted the mirror to say it was her, but it would reply with the name of another whom she hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Yasuri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.83,0:10:34.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Should the mirror have given that answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:38.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a mirror can talk in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:47.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the mirror answering, but rather the queen's true feelings responding to her vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:52.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If what you say is true then everything just becomes what you want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.76,0:10:54.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A holy man doesn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:56.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, cannot do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:00.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you humans who actually carry out tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:06.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't anything come to mind when I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:11.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant you saw me, you gave me this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Itezora Konayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:24.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiguchi Zanki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruga Meisai...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:51.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Itezora Konayuki, Nee-chan, Kiguchi Zanki, and Tsuruga Meisai, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:56.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lose to Tsuruga Meisai, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it was a harsh experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:07.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel regret and guilt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:18.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri-kun, looking at your own memories is recognizing the parts of you that you don't want to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:23.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,People change their memories to suit what they're most comfortable with.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.27,0:12:29.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that doesn't work with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:51.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point I've conveyed to you all that I needed to, so we'll part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:14.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're with me, you will have to face your darkest memories whether you want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:22.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the perspective of a holy man beyond human understanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:27.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You too will have to face the darkness you avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:35.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The 12 Maniwa Corps heads has been reduced to just two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:37.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should we do, Houou sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:43.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,With the loss of Oshidori, we have no choice but to continue on with our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We will head for Oushuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:52.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, we don't know when that man will make his appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is he, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:58.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he's a subordinate of Princess Hitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:14:00.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Hitei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:03.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Houou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:09.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Might you have any idea of who that man actually is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:18.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The way you've been talking about him, it sounds like you know him from long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:26.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea, but I'm sure I'm mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:28.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:34.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could still be alive, or that he'd be working under Princess Hitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:36.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a ninja of pride and respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This was before you were even born.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Ninja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, it can't be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:47.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That man died long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:53.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any ninja left who hold their head high, us included.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Pengin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:08.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.8}If we succeed at the negotiations with the strategian and manage to get all the Perfected Deviant Blades, we'll be retiring from active duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:13.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I must bear the responsibility for losing 10 of the 12 heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:16.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I will entrust the future of the clan to the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:18.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're joking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:24.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the only one left to hold the torch after I'm gone will be you, Pengin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.64,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am but a relic of the previous generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:31.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the strategian and Kyotouryuu and Princess Hitei...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:36.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, Shikizaki Kiki's Perfected Deviant Blades.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Houou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.80,0:15:43.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let us hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:47.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That masked man may attack at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yasuri-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You look bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:25.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming weaker when wielding a sword is almost like a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.80,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord6\3a&H88&\fs78\fad(600,0)\pos(648,89)}The day after winning Outou Nokogiri
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.80,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord6\3a&H88&\fs78\fad(600,0)\pos(648,700)}Shinou Issou Dojo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Bellflower!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.73,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs100\pos(1063,189)}Bellflower
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:15.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:20.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to keep up the act for a bit longer, but this is my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:24.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my loss, Shichika-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:27.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:33.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe I may have shone some light on your troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:42.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm saying is "To excel at an art is to excel at versatility".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for an amateur such as myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:48.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still put up some semblance of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:53.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1.6}You're saying it's strange that I'd get weaker by holding a training sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:58.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I used the word "curse".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:06.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just my intuition as a swordsman, but in the same way that the Shinou Issou school holds certain tenets at its core,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:12.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,your Kyotouryuu may also have certain core concepts that make it what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:16.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:28.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:30.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:42.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what happens when a sword tries to use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.47,0:18:47.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The complete inability to wield a sword is the nature of Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:15.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword can't use a sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:19.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the "curse" of Kyotouryuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.52,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Yasuri-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I want to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:31.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:35.44,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that your appearance and behavior are a projection from my memories, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:39.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did you get that arrogant personality from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:44.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that comes from how Togame-chan sees me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:47.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've taken a form from Togame's memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:49.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you two saw me at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:58.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My appearance and behavior are from your memories, and this personality is from hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So even Togame has something she's weak against?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has something difficult to deal with, or that they don't want to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:15.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something Togame finds difficult to deal with?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hida Takahito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hida Takahito?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:24.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that personality is exactly like my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:29.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That pompous manner of speech, those antics, that cavalier attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:33.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And to top it all, forcing me to do physical labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:38.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly the sort of thing that guy would do! {check __ }
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:53.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Recognize the parts of yourself that you don't want to face...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:59.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that my father is what came to mind upon returning here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:05.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In his dying breath, he told me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to have forgotten something so important...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:33.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that unpleasant woman is with Higaki Rinne around now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.77,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\bord3\3a&H88&\1c&HE1E1DA&\fs75\pos(346,170)}Owari Castle grounds
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:34.77,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\bord3\3a&H88&\1c&HE1E1DA&\fs75\pos(362,240)}Princess Hitei's Palace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Higaki Rinne the holy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, to entrust Seitou Hakari to that holy man of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very much like something you'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:47.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's there to get in the strategian's way?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mistaken here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:52.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm the one who gave it to Higaki Rinne.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:56.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, it's a bother for me as well that he has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:59.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, what happened with Dokutou Mekki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.09,0:22:05.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The most poisonous of Shikizaki Kiki's Deviant Blades, Dokutou Mekki...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:11.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For you to have failed at assassinating Maniwa Houou and let him run off with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I am dishonored.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:17.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokutou Mekki in the hands of Maniwa Houou...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:23.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I honestly have no idea if this'll bring misfortune or catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.06,0:22:27.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the strategian does manage to get a hold of Seitou Hakari,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.30,0:22:35.68,main,,0000,0000,0000,,the stage will finally be set for all of Shikizaki Kiki's 12 Perfected Deviant Blades to be assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:39.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The fulfillment of your ultimate desire is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:40.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:45.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who might be listening, so refrain from saying anything careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:53.77,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.8}The way you put it, it almost sounds like I'm the descendant of the legendary swordsmith Shikizaki Kiki who ruled over the Sengoku era,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.78,0:23:02.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and that I've have kept track of the Perfected Deviant Blades and stayed one step ahead of that unpleasant woman to collect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.36,0:23:06.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's totally not true of course, so there's no need to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:07.75,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:11.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, you are by no means Shikizaki Kiki's descendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:15.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies for saying something that might cause a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:18.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I am Princess Hitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:22.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I deny anything of myself outside of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.86,0:23:28.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I achieve my desire or not, I still deny it. {check __ }
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.49,0:23:30.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:33.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:37.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do it now, but could you look into something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:38.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What might that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.26,0:23:44.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I called the strategian and Kyotouryuu here not long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.43,0:23:50.06,main,,0000,0000,0000,,After I told them where Seitou Hakari was, Shichika-kun seemed kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:51.03,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs100\pos(645,122)\1c&HE7EBE7&}10 days ago
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:57.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seitou Hakari is somewhere around Hyakkeijou in Oushuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.09,0:24:00.33,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Its owner is the holy man Higaki Rinne.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:06.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the strategian?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:09.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unpleasant as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:13.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, that's her first time in Oushuu isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:15.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:20.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's part of the army, so wouldn't she be familiar with that area?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.36,0:24:26.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might just be my imagination, but I don't mind the idea of sending you out on a wild goose chase either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.64,0:24:31.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The relationship between Yasuri Shichika and Hyakkeijou...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.76,0:24:35.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's something to do with the strategian?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.46,0:24:37.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go find out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:38.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:43.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The two demonesses of the Owari Shogunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:48.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Real names unknown, history unknown—\nPrincess Hitei and the strategian Togame.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.15,0:24:53.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The day of their showdown is fast approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.31,0:24:58.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.90,0:25:03.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Higaki Rinne received Seitou Hakari from Shikizaki Kiki himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.23,0:25:06.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he got it as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.62,0:25:11.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you forget to tell me something as important as that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.05,0:25:14.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.51,0:25:18.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything else you forgot to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.83,0:25:21.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and and say so if there is!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.86,0:25:24.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you've forgotten something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:30.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't face the part of you that you're avoiding, you'll never remember. {check __ }
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.39,0:25:36.14,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's everything I forgot to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.04,0:25:38.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.43,0:25:42.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you intend to fight with Higaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.22,0:25:47.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine myself fighting him for no particular reason, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.45,0:25:48.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.79,0:25:53.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you asked me why I fight, I'd say I have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.89,0:25:56.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can find the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:59.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty straightforward, as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.20,0:26:03.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do find the answer to that, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.59,0:26:04.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.34,0:26:06.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.17,0:26:08.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.38,0:26:13.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a good experience for you to go toe to toe with a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:14.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.76,0:26:20.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just to let you know ahead of time, I am way weaker than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.01,0:26:23.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're already making excuses for losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.18,0:26:24.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.26,0:26:26.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win against people weaker than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.87,0:26:27.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.77,0:26:30.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we start then?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.79,0:26:34.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come whenever. Or just watch me go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.78,0:26:35.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.37,0:26:38.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:39.78,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs150\pos(905,154)}Kyotouryuu
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.12,0:26:39.78,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs150\pos(1128,298)}Lily
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.16,0:26:46.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.65,0:26:49.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.66,0:26:53.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Rose!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.72,0:26:54.38,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs110\pos(657,113)}Kyotouryuu    Rose
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:55.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoop, that's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.99,0:27:00.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.51,0:27:05.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.47,0:27:07.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from any of my fights up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:09.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't land anything on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.31,0:27:12.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going nowhere at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.11,0:27:16.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyotouryuu: Shichika Hachiretsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.90,0:27:17.57,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs100\pos(426,99)}Shichika Hachiretsu
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.29,0:27:19.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.16,0:27:26.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, that's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.44,0:27:30.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.73,0:27:33.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's not fighting at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.51,0:27:37.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He made the first move, yet he doesn't have any intention of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.33,0:27:53.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.98,0:27:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't face the part of you that you're avoiding,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.57,0:27:59.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll never remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.28,0:28:10.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.67,0:28:13.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think history is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:17.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that history is the proof that humans lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.67,0:28:20.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The proof that humans lived to their utmost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.41,0:28:23.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it looks and is the way it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.32,0:28:27.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, this history is very different from how it should have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.66,0:28:31.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent much time trying to correct those errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.51,0:28:34.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And for now, my role here is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.85,0:28:40.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point I've conveyed to you all that I needed to, so we'll part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.15,0:28:51.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide yourself here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.08,0:28:53.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not come out under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.69,0:28:58.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If history goes according to how I imagine, you will not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.76,0:29:02.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be the sole survivor in this cruel history to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.39,0:29:12.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai code says I should kill you, but even for the sake of correcting history, that is one thing I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.98,0:29:16.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot possibly kill my own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.06,0:29:21.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.13,0:29:24.87,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So the one who came to kill me was you after all, Mutsue-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.95,0:29:30.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I ... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.01,0:29:45.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.74,0:29:49.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you making me remember this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.38,0:30:03.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If your fighting strength is 10, mine would be around 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.00,0:30:06.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In a straight-up fight, I wouldn't even be a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.12,0:30:10.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, by this point you should be torn into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.41,0:30:16.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, your 10 strength is divided between offense and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.26,0:30:20.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, your attacking strength is only 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.42,0:30:27.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And so when I transfer all my strength into defense, your attacks cannot penetrate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.69,0:30:40.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to name Seitou Hakari's focus as a Deviant Blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.98,0:30:42.74,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: True defense
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.98,0:30:42.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd call it "Seitou Bouei".
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.74,0:30:43.36,OldKanji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs100\pos(618,115)}Seitou Bouei
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.40,0:30:46.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly does Seitou Hakari's focus do?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.01,0:30:48.59,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most true sword in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.59,0:30:50.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm its owner after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.95,0:30:52.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.31,0:30:54.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What part of you is "true"?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.04,0:30:57.79,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it's not fair to judge me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.34,0:31:00.92,main,,0000,0000,0000,,My current personality comes from Togame-chan, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.38,0:31:03.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, why am I putting up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't even a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:10.85,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so fun about giving me more memories I'd rather avoid?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.85,0:31:12.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.10,0:31:14.58,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love harassing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.58,0:31:18.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for this fight, you should be able to learn something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.60,0:31:23.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fighting is futile".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.35,0:31:26.86,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"There's no meaning to victory or defeat".
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.86,0:31:31.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame-chan said it would be a good experience for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.37,0:31:34.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,but any experience you get from fighting is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.74,0:31:38.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Any experience you'd get would only be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.42,0:31:44.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been fighting close by her for a year, but you don't seem to have learned anything from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.53,0:31:48.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,As kind-hearted as I am, I don't even feel like teaching you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.04,0:31:49.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.70,0:31:52.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She takes fighting too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.03,0:31:55.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like the concept of life itself is a fight for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.95,0:31:59.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What could her objective be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.23,0:32:03.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You may know it, but you don't see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.03,0:32:05.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just sympathize with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.24,0:32:06.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.53,0:32:07.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,—fell for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.93,0:32:13.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the way I see it, your feelings aren't anything like that of love. {check __ }
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.46,0:32:15.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:16.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.54,0:32:19.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you can calm yourself enough to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.79,0:32:28.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what Togame-chan's objective is, but I can tell you it's not something worth sacrificing herself for, much less others.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.27,0:32:35.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have realized that you've killed no small number of people over the course of your journey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.01,0:32:38.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Robbing people of their greatest purpose—life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.81,0:32:40.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.98,0:32:46.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuri-kun, people die when they are killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.98,0:32:51.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have been ignoring such a simple principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.54,0:32:56.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From my perspective, you, and of course Togame-chan, lack resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.41,0:33:00.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hakari" means "scales".
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.10,0:33:05.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to consider what you're doing and how it relates to everything around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.66,0:33:08.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell that to Togame-chan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.24,0:33:11.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.49,0:33:15.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll tell her next time she takes a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.35,0:33:17.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:22.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems she got tired and decided to take a break inside the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.35,0:33:23.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.98,0:33:29.19,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.98,0:33:43.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.92,0:33:51.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.99,0:33:56.18,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you fight so far as to sacrifice me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.43,0:34:02.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.51,0:34:03.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For Togame, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.23,0:34:17.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.17,0:34:19.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting for Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.43,0:34:23.47,main,,0000,0000,0000,,From the day I met Togame, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.89,0:34:40.67,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I see it, your feelings aren't anything like that of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.67,0:34:42.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget love or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.71,0:34:44.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I fight for Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.88,0:34:47.73,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for her, I wouldn't fight at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.73,0:34:49.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, Higaki Rinne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.44,0:34:57.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.45,0:34:59.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.04,0:35:02.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame! Togame!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.18,0:35:06.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichirin...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.97,0:35:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.31,0:35:09.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.92,0:35:13.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How was your fight with Higaki Rinne?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.36,0:35:15.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't really a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.74,0:35:17.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All he did was run.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.55,0:35:19.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.29,0:35:21.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He called it Seitou Bouei or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.29,0:35:23.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All his strength became defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.69,0:35:26.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that running from a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.71,0:35:29.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.91,0:35:36.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight is an agreement between two parties, so if your opponent abandons the fight, you can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.82,0:35:38.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.98,0:35:41.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a big problem with that strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.43,0:35:44.12,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can take advantage of that, we can defeat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.12,0:35:45.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it then?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.70,0:35:48.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally don't know what to do against a guy who can't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.23,0:35:50.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, think about it yourself a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.82,0:35:52.55,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.08,0:35:55.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.32,0:35:56.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.44,0:36:22.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.71,0:36:36.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.24,0:36:40.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember what my father's dying words were...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.35,0:36:46.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.19,0:37:02.40,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Seitou Hakari, no mistaking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.40,0:37:04.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You found it faster than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.62,0:37:08.08,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you did present that strange riddle through Shichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.08,0:37:10.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you realized something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.70,0:37:19.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had kept your offensive mindset while continuing to dig, would you have thought that hilt and blade was Seitou Hakari?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.00,0:37:20.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I probably wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.11,0:37:24.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seitou Hakari is a sword upon which you weigh yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.53,0:37:26.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a sword that cuts people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.37,0:37:31.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a sword that cuts oneself, tests oneself, and knows oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.91,0:37:33.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why it is bladeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.90,0:37:35.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say it is swordless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.36,0:37:37.27,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.27,0:37:39.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes sense if you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.61,0:37:43.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-1.4}A Japanese sword is not something you can safely preserve underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.76,0:37:46.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it doesn't have a blade to preserve, then there's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.96,0:37:51.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really a fan of that way of reverse thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.49,0:37:54.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.17,0:37:58.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That annoying personality is exactly like that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.32,0:38:01.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is "that man"? Mind telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.32,0:38:04.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.34,0:38:06.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,...father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.48,0:38:08.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you his name though.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.05,0:38:09.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.30,0:38:11.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you didn't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.36,0:38:13.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you hostile to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.72,0:38:15.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Completely the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.78,0:38:18.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I live for the sake of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:21.82,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You could even say this sword collection is for his sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.82,0:38:24.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're uncomfortable with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.43,0:38:28.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you admitted that, you found Hakari.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.04,0:38:31.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And despite avoiding you, you stand before me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.66,0:38:36.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder though, why didn't Yasuri-kun try to have another go at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.96,0:38:40.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could figure out a way to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.62,0:38:45.31,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shichika used all his combat strength on defense, what would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.31,0:38:48.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't even have a fight, never mind a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.98,0:38:57.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, by abandoning offense, even without winning, the result will be effectively victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.49,0:38:58.56,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.09,0:39:03.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The essence of a sword is its blade, something that doesn't bend or break, and cuts well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.60,0:39:06.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I had always thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.71,0:39:11.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But without a blade, you don't even need a sheath to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.74,0:39:17.20,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can hold it with resolve, all you need are its hilt and guard to be able to face yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.59,0:39:19.04,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.04,0:39:20.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.96,0:39:23.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job discerning that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.02,0:39:25.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart, Togame-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.34,0:39:30.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Having someone with the body of a little girl patronizing me like that really annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.07,0:39:37.51,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Higaki, as a reward for figuring it out, will you answer one question of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.51,0:39:39.99,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll answer as many as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.99,0:39:44.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you received Seitou Hakari from Shikizaki Kiki himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.43,0:39:46.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of man was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.69,0:39:49.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he was a denying kind of guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.81,0:39:51.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Denying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.01,0:39:53.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard that somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.09,0:39:58.21,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I said I was a friend, but it's been so long that I've forgotten quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.21,0:40:02.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But apparently he saw the profoundness of himself in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.10,0:40:08.17,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And eventually, he denied what he didn't want to face, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:11.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not before pushing Seitou Hakari onto me though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.39,0:40:13.88,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He was endlessly troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.88,0:40:18.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't want to get poisoned by it, so I buried it pretty quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.60,0:40:21.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so it wasn't recently that you buried it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.22,0:40:23.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope, I did that right after I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.98,0:40:30.13,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then they built a castle on top of it, and then that castle burned down, and then they turned it into an execution ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.13,0:40:32.60,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The eras sure fly by.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.60,0:40:34.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.41,0:40:40.39,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Seitou Hakari was buried here before Hida Castle was even built...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.39,0:40:43.96,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how my father saw the distortion of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.79,0:40:49.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then to correct that history he drew his bow against the Owari Shogunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.71,0:40:51.89,main,,0000,0000,0000,,And then made the ultimate sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.70,0:40:59.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He put all his friends and family on the line to draw that bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.02,0:41:00.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of history...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.94,0:41:07.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, he must have felt that the completion of the forging of Shikizaki Kiki's Deviant Blades was almost at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.48,0:41:08.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Completion?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.78,0:41:10.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:13.90,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Perfected" Deviant Blades have already been perfected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.90,0:41:14.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.69,0:41:18.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've been taking Yasuri-kun along with you all this time without even knowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.10,0:41:19.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.24,0:41:21.37,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How shocking....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.37,0:41:26.49,main,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you not know that after crafting the 12 Perfected Deviant Blades,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.49,0:41:33.01,main,,0000,0000,0000,,he went on to forge his final and ultimate \NCompleted Deviant Blade, "Kyotou Yasuri"?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.88,0:41:37.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shichika is one of Shikizaki Kiki's swords?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.15,0:41:42.26,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not Yasuri-kun precisely, but rather Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.26,0:41:47.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why Sabi Hakuhei referred to him as a relic of Shikizaki Kiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.53,0:41:50.94,main,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Shichika was of Kiki's bloodline, and that Sabi himself was a failed creation...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.23,0:41:57.57,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not so much "bloodline" as "swordline".
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.70,0:41:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs150\pos(982,220)}Bloodline
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.66,0:41:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs150\pos(302,602)}Swordline
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:42:03.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Shikizaki Kiki and the Kyotouryuu founder Yasuri Kazune were from the same generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.91,0:42:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means there was some connection between the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.24,0:42:12.25,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Was Shikizaki Kiki involved in the formation of Kyotouryuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.25,0:42:15.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Completed Deviant Blade Kyotou Yasuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.15,0:42:17.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're swordless?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.55,0:42:23.10,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm taking Seitou Hakari.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.44,0:42:27.53,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.53,0:42:36.36,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to understand your strategy of forcing a match to a draw by neither winning nor losing, all for the sake of your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.36,0:42:40.70,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely... not quite right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.98,0:42:44.15,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must throw away objectives for the sake of your objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.15,0:42:47.11,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the lesson you needed to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.11,0:42:49.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ambition, aspirations, vengeance...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.63,0:42:52.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You must throw aside all these objectives for the sake of your true objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.84,0:42:55.65,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.65,0:43:00.84,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can throw away everything but my objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.82,0:43:10.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after conquering what you couldn't face before, you still retain that stubborn streak.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.23,0:43:11.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.23,0:43:14.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the way you live then you can just force your way through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.60,0:43:19.61,main,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what were your father's last words?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.46,0:43:23.91,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.18,0:43:26.93,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The words of a father to his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.93,0:43:29.80,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially considering how cute a daughter I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.80,0:43:31.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.30,0:43:33.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.07,0:43:36.76,main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you very much."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.30,0:43:40.72,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think I'd be able to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.31,0:44:36.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm one of the Deviant Blades that Shikizaki Kiki made, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.89,0:44:42.09,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally don't feel it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.09,0:44:48.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well to be precise, the Completed Deviant Blade isn't you yourself, but rather Kyotouryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.75,0:44:53.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The founder Yasuri Kazune, your father Yasuri Mutsue,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.41,0:44:59.34,main,,0000,0000,0000,,and even your sister Yasuri Nanami were all the Completed Deviant Blade "Kyotou Yasuri".
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.87,0:45:03.48,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I feel it doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.48,0:45:06.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like, "who cares?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.05,0:45:08.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty easygoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.00,0:45:10.02,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You should bear some troubles in mind at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.02,0:45:12.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess that's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.98,0:45:20.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So maybe the fact that I can't use swords is the curse that Shikizaki Kiki bestowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.07,0:45:22.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.78,0:45:25.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eitherways, there are only two left, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.42,0:45:28.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream is almost within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.66,0:45:30.66,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.66,0:45:35.43,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything at all about Dokutou Mekki or Entou Jyuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.43,0:45:36.46,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.80,0:45:46.30,main,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about "dreams" or "objectives", I feel like that holy man's going to appear out of nowhere again.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.30,0:45:49.05,main,,0000,0000,0000,,You really aren't good at dealing with him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.05,0:45:50.71,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't ever want to meet him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.09,0:45:54.98,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.98,0:45:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs120\1c&H000000&\bord1\pos(858,628)}Dewa
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.98,0:45:58.81,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already at Dewa, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.81,0:46:01.78,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, why don't we pass through the Shougi town on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.25,0:46:04.74,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.74,0:46:07.03,main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can see Kiguchi Zanki?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.03,0:46:07.95,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.27,0:46:09.45,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do mean "huh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.45,0:46:10.41,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheerio!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.17,0:46:14.63,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your jealous streak is really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.63,0:46:18.83,main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get back to Owari as fast as possible, so we can't go through the Shougi town!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.23,0:46:20.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,For your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.54,0:46:21.50,main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.81,0:46:24.38,main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting for your sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.38,0:46:25.97,main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the answer I gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.97,0:46:38.32,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Togame, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.74,0:46:49.54,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.56,0:46:53.24,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.56,0:47:00.00,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sword wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.00,0:47:02.29,main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.56,0:47:05.42,main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.42,0:47:07.22,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.90,0:47:13.16,main,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what happens to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.16,0:47:16.69,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But please save Houou-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.83,0:47:21.23,main,,0000,0000,0000,,The strategian and the Maniwa Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.92,0:47:26.28,main,,0000,0000,0000,,They have allied, they have fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.28,0:47:30.07,main,,0000,0000,0000,,But the final hour of their destiny together has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.74,0:47:36.62,main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fsp-0.5}The story of Katanagatari on this month and this evening ends here.
